{"doc_urls":["windows_tips.html#windows-小技巧","inactivated_windows_change_combine_taskbar_buttons.html#未激活的-windows-修改合并任务栏按钮"],"index":{"documentStore":{"docInfo":{"0":{"body":1,"breadcrumbs":2,"title":1},"1":{"body":20,"breadcrumbs":3,"title":1}},"docs":{"0":{"body":"Windows 算是本人接触最早，也是使用时间最长的操作系统了。 系统的可视化操作固然强大，但是调优使用方面还是比较麻烦，于是在此记录一些使用技巧。","breadcrumbs":"Windows 小技巧 » Windows 小技巧","id":"0","title":"Windows 小技巧"},"1":{"body":"Windows 10 未激活的时候，虽然可以使用，但是一些个性化功能无法调整，比如无法修改“合并任务栏按钮”的方式。 鉴于使用的是虚拟机，购买激活码也不合适，所以找了一下其他方法来解决。 按下 win + R，输入 regedit，打开 注册表编辑器。 打开目录 HKEY_CURRENT_USER\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Explorer\\Advanced。 根据个人需求，按照下表新建或调整数据。 Key Type Value Notice TaskbarGlomLevel REG_DWORD 2 主屏任务栏按钮不合并 MMTaskbarGlomLevel REG_DWORD 2 多显示器其他任务栏按钮不合并 MMTaskbarMode REG_DWORD 2 多显示器其他任务栏只显示打开的程序 注册表编辑器的内容修改后，打开 任务管理器，点击 进程，找到 Windows 资源管理器，右键选中，点击 重新启动。 此后即可生效。","breadcrumbs":"Windows 小技巧 » 未激活的 Windows 修改任务栏的堆叠 » 未激活的 Windows 修改“合并任务栏按钮”","id":"1","title":"未激活的 Windows 修改“合并任务栏按钮”"}},"length":2,"save":true},"fields":["title","body","breadcrumbs"],"index":{"body":{"root":{"1":{"0":{"df":1,"docs":{"1":{"tf":1.0}}},"df":0,"docs":{}},"2":{"df":1,"docs":{"1":{"tf":1.7320508075688772}}},"df":0,"docs":{},"h":{"df":0,"docs":{},"k":{"df":0,"docs":{},"e":{"df":0,"docs":{},"y":{"_":{"c":{"df":0,"docs":{},"u":{"df":0,"docs":{},"r":{"df":0,"docs":{},"r":{"df":0,"docs":{},"e":{"df":0,"docs":{},"n":{"df":0,"docs":{},"t":{"_":{"df":0,"docs":{},"u":{"df":0,"docs":{},"s":{"df":0,"docs":{},"e":{"df":0,"docs":{},"r":{"\\":{"df":0,"docs":{},"s":{"df":0,"docs":{},"o":{"df":0,"docs":{},"f":{"df":0,"docs":{},"t":{"df":0,"docs":{},"w":{"a":{"df":0,"docs":{},"r":{"df":0,"docs":{},"e":{"\\":{"df":0,"docs":{},"m":{"df":0,"docs":{},"i":{"c":{"df":0,"docs":{},"r":{"df":0,"docs":{},"o":{"df":0,"docs":{},"s":{"df":0,"docs":{},"o":{"df":0,"docs":{},"f":{"df":0,"docs":{},"t":{"\\":{"df":0,"docs":{},"w":{"df":0,"docs":{},"i":{"df":0,"docs":{},"n":{"d":{"df":0,"docs":{},"o":{"df":0,"doc